item.title: U.S.A.F. Thunderbird Pilot to Make Advance Visit for NY Air Show ⋆ Hudson Valley News Network
item.description:
U.S.A.F. Thunderbird Pilot to Make Advance Visit for NY Air Show ⋆ Hudson Valley News Network

Orange County, NY - One of the pilots from the U.S. Air Force Thunderbirds will make an advance visit to Stewart International Airport on January 22 nd to plan the team's performance at the 2016 New York Air Show over Labor Day weekend.
